name: One Track
description:
This is for the mastering of one track.

The stereo .wav file should be emailed to lofthousemastering@gmail.com.
It will then be mastered overnight, given a professional sheen and make it sound commercial and radio friendly.
The track will then be sent back with an audio watermark at various points, and if the track is satisfactory, you pay for the track here and the un-watermarked version will be sent immediately.
